-- MOVES-Natixis names Alex Chang managing director for Taiwan
-- 
-- Mon Oct 06, 2014 04:18AM EDT
-- None



Oct 6 (Reuters) - French bank Natixis Global Asset Management <CNAT.PA> appointed Alex Chang as managing director and head of its Taiwan business.

Chang joined the bank on Sept. 15. He reports to Kinji Kato, executive managing director and head of Natixis in Japan. Chang is responsible for business initiatives across the institutional, wholesale and retail channels.